data.enText: a person who is starting to learn sth and cannot do it very well yet

tr: a person who founds or establishes some institution
example: George Washington is the father of his country

tr: someone new to a field or activity

value.def: A beginner is someone who has just started learning to do something and cannot do it very well yet.

example.ex: The course is suitable for beginners and advanced students...
example.tran: 这门课程适合初学者和高级程度的学生。

example.ex: I am a complete beginner to bird-keeping.
example.tran: 在养鸟方面，我完全是一个新手。

trans: 二次初学者，非真实初学者(对某一语言虽已有基本知识但又从头学习)
